text: 2077 (MMLXXVII), the 2077th year of the Common Era (CE) and Anno Domini (AD) designations, . == Events == * May 15: 150th anniversary of the Hollywood Roosevelt Hotel. * May 18: 150th anniversary of the Grauman's Chinese Theatre. * May 25: 100th anniversary of the Star Wars. * An annular solar eclipse will occur at the Moon's descending node of orbit on Monday, November 15, 2077. ==References== Category:2070s
